","text":"These are the names of the sons of Israel who came to Egypt "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 1:1–5","book":"Exo","chapter":1,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 26:4","book":"Num","chapter":26,"verse":4,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" —Jacob and his sons:"},{"kind":"text","text":" Jacob’s firstborn: Reuben."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 1:1–5","book":"Exo","chapter":1,"verse":1},{"label":"Nm 26:4","book":"Num","chapter":26,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:46:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Reuben’s sons: "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 6:14","book":"Exo","chapter":6,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" Hanoch, Pallu, Hezron, and Carmi."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 6:14","book":"Exo","chapter":6,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:46:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Simeon’s sons: "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 6:15","book":"Exo","chapter":6,"verse":15,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" Jemuel, Jamin, Ohad, Jachin, Zohar, and Shaul, the son of a Canaanite woman."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 6:15","book":"Exo","chapter":6,"verse":15}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:46:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Levi’s sons: "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 6:16","book":"Exo","chapter":6,"verse":16,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Ch 6:16","book":"1Ch","chapter":6,"verse":16,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" Gershon, Kohath, and Merari."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 6:16","book":"Exo","chapter":6,"verse":16},{"label":"1Ch 6:16","book":"1Ch","chapter":6,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:46:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Judah’s sons: Er, Onan, Shelah, Perez, and Zerah; but Er and Onan died in the land of Canaan."},{"kind":"text","text":" The sons "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 38:29","book":"Gen","chapter":38,"verse":29,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Ch 2:5","book":"1Ch","chapter":2,"verse":5,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" of Perez were Hezron and Hamul."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 38:29","book":"Gen","chapter":38,"verse":29},{"label":"1Ch 2:5","book":"1Ch","chapter":2,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:46:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Issachar’s sons: "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Ch 7:1","book":"1Ch","chapter":7,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" Tola, Puvah, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Sam, Syr read Puah; 1Ch 7:1"},{"kind":"text","text":" Jashub, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Sam, LXX; MT reads Iob"},{"kind":"text","text":" and Shimron."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Ch 7:1","book":"1Ch","chapter":7,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Sam, Syr read Puah; 1Ch 7:1"},{"marker":2,"text":"Sam, LXX; MT reads Iob"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:46:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Zebulun’s sons: Sered, Elon, and Jahleel."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:46:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"These were Leah’s sons born to Jacob in Paddan-aram, as well as his daughter Dinah. The total number of persons: "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit All persons his sons and his daughters:"},{"kind":"text","text":" thirty-three."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit All persons his sons and his daughters:"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:46:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Gad’s sons: Ziphion, Haggi, Shuni, Ezbon, Eri, Arodi, and Areli."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:46:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Asher’s sons: "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Ch 7:30–31","book":"1Ch","chapter":7,"verse":30,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" Imnah, Ishvah, Ishvi, Beriah, and their sister Serah."},{"kind":"text","text":" Beriah’s sons were Heber and Malchiel."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Ch 7:30–31","book":"1Ch","chapter":7,"verse":30}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:46:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"These were the sons of Zilpah —whom Laban gave to his daughter Leah —that she bore to Jacob: sixteen persons."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:46:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The sons of Jacob’s wife Rachel: Joseph and Benjamin."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:46:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Manasseh and Ephraim were born to Joseph in the land of Egypt. They were born to him by Asenath daughter of Potiphera, a priest at On. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or Heliopolis"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or Heliopolis"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:46:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Benjamin’s sons: "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 26:38","book":"Num","chapter":26,"verse":38,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Ch 7:6–12","book":"1Ch","chapter":7,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Ch 8:1","book":"1Ch","chapter":8,"verse":1,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" Bela, Becher, Ashbel, Gera, Naaman, Ehi, Rosh, Muppim, Huppim, and Ard."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Nm 26:38","book":"Num","chapter":26,"verse":38},{"label":"1Ch 7:6–12","book":"1Ch","chapter":7,"verse":6},{"label":"1Ch 8:1","book":"1Ch","chapter":8,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:46:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"These were Rachel’s sons who were born to Jacob: fourteen persons."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:46:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Dan’s son: "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Alt Hb tradition reads sons:"},{"kind":"text","text":" Hushim."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Alt Hb tradition reads sons:"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:46:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Naphtali’s sons: "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Ch 7:13","book":"1Ch","chapter":7,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" Jahzeel, Guni, Jezer, and Shillem."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Ch 7:13","book":"1Ch","chapter":7,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:46:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"These were the sons of Bilhah, whom Laban gave to his daughter Rachel. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 29:29","book":"Gen","chapter":29,"verse":29,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 30:5–8","book":"Gen","chapter":30,"verse":5,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" She bore to Jacob: seven persons."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 29:29","book":"Gen","chapter":29,"verse":29},{"label":"Gn 30:5–8","book":"Gen","chapter":30,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:46:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The total number of persons belonging to Jacob —his direct descendants, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit Jacob who came out from his loins"},{"kind":"text","text":" not including the wives of Jacob’s sons —who came to Egypt: sixty-six."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit Jacob who came out from his loins"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:46:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And Joseph’s sons who were born to him in Egypt: two persons."},{"kind":"text","text":" All those of Jacob’s household who came to Egypt: seventy "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"LXX reads 75; Ac 7:14"},{"kind":"text","text":" persons. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 1:5","book":"Exo","chapter":1,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 10:22","book":"Deu","chapter":10,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 7:14","book":"Act","chapter":7,"verse":14,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 1:5","book":"Exo","chapter":1,"verse":5},{"label":"Dt 10:22","book":"Deu","chapter":10,"verse":22},{"label":"Ac 7:14","book":"Act","chapter":7,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"LXX reads 75; Ac 7:14"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:46:28","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Now Jacob had sent Judah ahead of him to Joseph to prepare for his arrival "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit to give directions before him"},{"kind":"text","text":" at Goshen. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 45:10","book":"Gen","chapter":45,"verse":10,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" When they came to the land of Goshen, "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 45:10","book":"Gen","chapter":45,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit to give directions before him"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:46:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Joseph hitched the horses to his chariot and went up to Goshen to meet his father Israel. Joseph presented himself to him, threw his arms around him, and wept for a long time. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 45:14","book":"Gen","chapter":45,"verse":14,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 45:14","book":"Gen","chapter":45,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:46:30","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Then Israel said to Joseph, “I’m ready to die now because I have seen your face and you are still alive!”"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:46:31","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Joseph said to his brothers and to his father’s family, “I will go up and inform Pharaoh, telling him, ‘My brothers and my father’s family, who were in the land of Canaan, have come to me. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 47:1","book":"Gen","chapter":47,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 47:1","book":"Gen","chapter":47,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:46:32","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The men are shepherds; they also raise livestock. They have brought their flocks and herds and all that they have.’ "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:46:33","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"When Pharaoh addresses you and asks, ‘What is your occupation?’ "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Gen:46:34","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"you are to say, ‘Your servants, both we and our ancestors, have raised livestock "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit fathers, are men of livestock"},{"kind":"text","text":" from our youth until now.’ Then you will be allowed to settle in the land of Goshen, since all shepherds are detestable to Egyptians.” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 43:32","book":"Gen","chapter":43,"verse":32,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 8:26","book":"Exo","chapter":8,"verse":26,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 43:32","book":"Gen","chapter":43,"verse":32},{"label":"Ex 8:26","book":"Exo","chapter":8,"verse":26}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit fathers, are men of livestock"}]}]},"cachedAt":1783279314420}